{"tid":2236771,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"劉細良：指控 教協 抗爭不力及貪戀議席的人，是想協助中共，鬥死教協！","createTime":"2020-10-09T17:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T14:14:37.000Z","uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fd3e0ecc5598250efe63e85423f7c54cbb139d62","tid":2236771,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uC9VLkYHiw0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuC9VLkYHiw0&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzlSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=7fd6ae63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uC9VLkYHiw0</a><br />\n<br />\n26:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉細良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n教協係司徒華支聯會㗎嘛，所以係左派入邊從來都係以鬥倒教協作為目標，但係因為過往教協係教師嘅支持度高，所以一路都打唔入。 用咗好多方法㗎啦，拉人出嚟又有，共產黨滲透又有，幾十年來都打唔入。 所以而家決定夾硬嚟，用最粗暴嘅手法DQ老師，睇你教協點回應。 <br />\n<br />\n如果教協做唔到嘢嘅話就會有<span class=\"red\">另一首嘅攻擊「教協有咩用呀你」，兩邊夾架，網上面一樣好多人鬧緊教協「你教協冇用，只係識得貪戀10皮人工！」 兩邊一齊夾死教協！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"bb2c80fa108882f2b742c5ab2b5efeaf278d7d67","tid":2236771,"uid":257516,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"係人都知教協廢到無倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本只係一間超級市場 藍屍都幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abac582b6d1b583d06621a9e20e7b64553f44db","tid":2236771,"uid":143499,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"285323c74668e3ca8be5d372f4de699648eb425f","tid":2236771,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:17:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fbd219700414921dcc26dba37bd10694dd813f6","tid":2236771,"uid":18995,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"曾任香港政府屬下的中央政策組全職顧問嘅劉細良 劉国師<br />\n呢啲過街老鼠唔好躝出嚟維穩啦<br />\n躝翻入九龍灣整頭套同antony 69互丁算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"